  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will be conducted to evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of AVP-786,
      as compared with placebo, for the treatment of negative symptoms of schizophrenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
